    "Both of these gates are trained to save information from the past or remove information that is irrelevant to the prediction.Here, the update gate Z k, the reset gate r k, the cell State C k and the new State h k are mathematically formulated as follows:Z k σ (w z h k-1 + U z x k) (10) r k σ (w r h k-1 + U r x k) (11) C k tanh(w c r k + w c h k-1 + U c x k) (12) h k (z k C k) + (h k-1 -z k h k-1) (13)x k is the input, h k is the hidden layer output, w s are the cell state weights and U s are the bias terms.",
